version_description: Time signature is 3/4. It contains parts that are played by the piano (G - Gmaj7 - G6 - G). Try playing this version from beginning til end with arpeggio. Highest e string should be used only when D chords are played. You can also substitute the G at the end of the verse with an Em.

version_description: Changes compared to Version #1: 1. Missing sections: need to add the "Mmmmm" sections at the end of Verse 3 and the end of the song. 2. There is no chorus after Verses 1 and 4. Only after Verses 2 and 3. 3. A7 should be A. 4. Should be an F above "never" in the chorus. 5. End of the chorus could be A, Asus4, A. 6. D should replace Bm in second line of every verse.

5-star doesn't mean it's good, no matter how many votes. I have checked all the other versions. Version 3 and 5 are close, but still has a lot of the chords completely wrong. This tab is pretty much perfect. Couldn't find an accurate version with the Ebmaj7, G7/D, D7's and the Fsus. The other versions have got a Gm instead of Ebmaj7 which sounds awful. Play the song yourself and you'll see. Same goes with the Csus to G... it's acutally a Fsus to G. not to mention the "chorus"
